Check out this quick #90s inspired #bellahadid updo I recreated on my client this week!  I prepped the hair by blow drying in @theouai wave spray.  I created a deep side part and sectioned out the bang area.  I then applied @theouai matte pomade and @bumbleandbumble spray de mode to the roots of the hair all over the entire head.  I then gathered the hair with my @masonpearsonbros brush and twisted the hair up with my hands.  I then secured with large French hair pins.  Next i flat ironed the ends sticking out and sprayed with hairspray for a spikey look.  #90shair #90shairstyle #updo #hairbyalexbrown

Showing you one of my fav ways to wave hair on the beach wave 👸🏼 @elle_ferguson !  I call this technique a “twist”. Start with the iron close to the scalp curling away from the face and without opening the clamp, let the hair twist out the end of the iron and continue to drag and twist the iron down the hair strand, leaving the ends straight.  This will give you a much more loose, effortless looking wave.  Im using my @ghd_northamerica 1.25” iron and finish with my most recent fav @renefurtererusa Texture Spray ✨#hairbyalexbrown

Comin in hot with months of content😅😅 Not gonna lie..figuring out how to dress this new body has been a struggle lol a lot of you asked how I could keep it hidden for so long and it’s because all I wear is oversized/baggy clothes!  It’s comfortable and luckily the trend rn..figuring it out, but man pregnancy is a trip!🙃🥰

We are so grateful for all of the love and kindness we are getting from everyone🥹

To those of you who have noticed or wondered over the last 6 months, thank you for not asking 😂and giving us time to share when we felt ready! ..And to anyone out there yearning to be parents, struggling with infertility, the loss of a child or of someone who could have made you a parent, my heart is with you and I know seeing posts like mine are not easy.  It is something I think about often and have put into consideration when announcing our news.  Never forget that social media is the highlight reel of our lives and not always the full picture! Sending you love and peace. ❤️ Alex

We are so excited to welcome @ashleyyounghair to @spacebyalexbrown!  I’ve known Ashley since 2009 and have always been in awe of how booked,  busy, and talented she is. (I actually attended @jenatkinhair class with her in Toronto too before I moved to LA!)

Ashley specializes in women’s haircuts and styling, updos, and keratin treatments.  She also has become a well-established wedding hair stylist not only doing bridal hair in Chicago but she has had the honor to do weddings all over the world.

After being in the industry for almost 20 years, Ashley has established herself as a top stylist in Chicago.  Ashley has completed several courses by great stylists such as Jen Atkin, Priscilla Valles, Chris McMillan, and Chris Appleton to name a few.  Ashley is influenced by celebrities and the everyday woman. She continues to stay inspired by giving each of her clients a chic and effortless look as well as transformations. 

Give her a follow and book with her directly at the link in her bio! Welcome Ashley!! 🎉

4 months tomorrow with my Gigi 🥹🫶🏼 #firsttimemom #babygirl #4monthsold #gigi #giorgiagray

4 months in as a mom and I must say things are looking up 😅. Gigi is smiling and giggling and I’m obsessed with this last month! (The first 2-3 were real ROUGH and we don’t remember much🥲) I’m starting to settle into my new identity, learning to plan on leaving the house 45 min earlier than I actually need to so I’m right on time.. figuring all of the things out slowly.  My body however still feels ancient and my left hip won’t cooperate, but the hormones are balancing and I actually don’t remember the last time I cried which is a MIRACLE in itself 🤪🙏🏼She is now almost rolling over, smiling at herself in the mirror(and me in the car mirror!), drinking loads of formula and my nipples have healed praise God above😂. I’m in love with dressing her and combing her hair (the little she has left lol) and bath time.  She’s the best girl in the whole world and I’m so HAPPY to be on this journey..everyday is more exciting than the previous…and we’re just getting started 🫶🏼 happy 4 months Giorgia Gray!!!🥳🤩 I LOVE YOU SOULMATE
